  "keyFeatures": [
    "ESC/POS command generation from a structured TypeScript/JavaScript API",
    "Cross-platform support: Linux, macOS, Windows (CUPS/WinAPI) and Android (Bluetooth SPP)",
    "16 printable section types: text, tables, QR codes, barcodes, images, and more",
    "Flexible character encoding via encoding_rs with accent-removal fallback",
    "Builder helper functions for zero-boilerplate section construction",
    "Tauri v2 permission system integration",
    "Floyd-Steinberg dithering for monochrome image printing",
    "Multiple paper sizes from 40mm to 104mm with automatic char/pixel helpers"
  ],
